description:
In this episode, the team discusses stocks with award-winning financial journalist, television news anchor, New York Times best selling author, and host of the Money Rehab podcast, Nicole Lapin.

Follow Nicole on Instagram and Twitter @nicolelapin !

Make sure to check out the Money Rehab podcast wherever you listen to podcasts!
